
  ///////////////////////////////////////
    Usurper 0.24 - Upgrade Information 
  ///////////////////////////////////////

We are not providing upgrade programs from old versions of Usurper.

If you are running Usurper 0.20e:
-extract this archive into your game directory
-run the editor and reset monster files


--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Upgrading from a version below v0.20e
    Download Usurper 0.23 or 0.18 version. In these archives you will find 
    appropriate converters for older versions.
